data.description: Don't wait, own this four year old Oakwood home today! The owners didn't skimp on the upgrades when they built it - quartz counters, scratch resistant LVP flooring, wood cabinets with soft close doors and drawers and tile backsplash just to name a few. Walk in to an open-concept floor plan, seamlessly connecting the living room and kitchen. The large kitchen island is an ideal space for entertaining full of storage with high-end stainless steel appliances, pantry and tons of natural light it would be hard not to want to cook here. Make your way upstairs to a luxurious primary suite, complete with large walk-in closet and ensuite bathroom featuring a walk-in shower and dual vanities. Two additional bedrooms, upgraded full bath and convenient laundry room make up the rest of the second floor. The top floor includes a versatile loft area, offering additional living space for work or play. Also included on the top floor is guest bedroom and full bath, perfect for out of town guests or family member that need some extra privacy. A low maintenance yard with custom built shed and dog house make outdoor life easy. Two car attached finished garage, sprinkler system, security system, low HOA and solar panels complete this home. Reunion's community amenities, including parks, trails, and a recreation center along with shopping centers and restaurants will make daily life a breeze. Close to E470, I70, DIA, Buckley Space Force Base and Anschutz Hospital. This home has an assumable 30 year mortgage at 3.125% with a loan balance of approximately $365,000! Schedule your showing today!
